data.description: Welcome to 9600 Heartwood Ln! This beautiful, Well-kept home is located in the highly desirable Mint Hill. With 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this home is everything you've been searching for. The large yard and on cul de sac lot give the home an attractive curb appeal. As you enter the home through the foyer, the main level is lovely featuring a dedicated dining room, breakfast nook that opens up to the kitchen, laundry room, half bath, a formal living room, and a multifunctional den. Upstairs is the primary bedroom suite and two nicely sized secondary bedrooms. Enjoy your summer evenings outdoors on the patio in the massive backyard. This property is perfect for anyone looking for convenience, outdoor living, and lots of space! HOME IS BEING SOLD "AS IS" with no known Issues.
